Package commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutAction
    Action to display information about the game.
    AccelerateCarAction
    Action to accelerate the player's car.
    AddFuelCanAction
    Action to add a FuelCan to the game world.
    AddOilSlickAction
    Action to add an oil slick to the game world.
    AddPylonAction
    Action to add a pylon to the game world.
    AdvanceGameTimeAction
    Action to advance the game time by a tick.
    BrakeCarAction
    Action to brake the player's car.
    ChangeStrategiesAction
    Action to change the strategies of strategic game objects.
    CollideWithBirdAction
    Action which represents a collision between the player's car and a bird in the game world.
    CollideWithCarAction
    Action which represents a collision between the player's car and a non-player car.
    CollideWithFuelCanAction
    Action that represents the player's car picking up a fuel can.
    CollideWithPylonAction
    Action that represents a racer colliding with a pylon along the track.
    Command
    A convenience class for command labels to use about the game code.
    DeleteSelectedAction
    Action to delete selected objects from the game world.
    DisplayActionMessage
    Action to display a message for features not yet implemented.
    GenerateNewColorsAction
    Action for changing the color of all game objects which are "color-able".
    MusicStateAction
    Action to keep the background music state correct.
    QuitAction
    Action to verify and handle if the user wants to quit the game.
    SetSoundAction
    Action to control the game world's sound state.
    SteerCarLeftAction
    Action for steering the player's car left.
    SteerCarRightAction
    Action for steering the player's car right.
    SwitchModeAction
